'''明福俠'''是[[香港|香港]]藝人[[黎明|黎明]]創作的一個虛構人物，人物造型參考自[[蝙蝠俠|蝙蝠俠]]，於2016年在社交網站平台首度亮相<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20160409/00282_013.html|title = 黎明變蝙蝠俠任超人魚肉|publisher = 東方日報 |date = 2016-04-09 |accessdate =2020-02-07|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160815140445/https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20160409/00282_013.html|archive-date =2016-08-15|dead-url =no}}</ref>。黎明最初以明福俠身份出現，是為了宣傳《[[黎明Leon_30th_Anniversary_Random_Love_Songs_4D_in_Live_2016|黎明Leon 30th Anniversary Random Love Songs 4D in Live 2016]]》演唱會，後來不時以此人物身份與網民互動及交代工作近況，並參與廣告拍攝及演唱歌曲<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1628517/%E6%98%8E%E7%A6%8F%E4%BF%A0%E9%9C%B2%E7%9C%9F%E8%BA%AB%E5%80%92%E5%90%8A%E6%8B%8D%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%20%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%E8%AE%9A%E9%AC%BC%E9%A6%AC|title = 明福俠露真身倒吊拍廣告 粉絲讚鬼馬|publisher = 晴報 |date = 2016-11-07 |accessdate =2020-02-06|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20200206112026/https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1628517/%E6%98%8E%E7%A6%8F%E4%BF%A0%E9%9C%B2%E7%9C%9F%E8%BA%AB%E5%80%92%E5%90%8A%E6%8B%8D%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%20%E7%B2%89%E7%B5%B2%E8%AE%9A%E9%AC%BC%E9%A6%AC|archive-date =2020-02-06|dead-url =no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language = zh |author = 胡劍威 | url = https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/34000/%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87-%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E5%8C%96%E8%BA%AB-%E6%98%8E%E7%A6%8F%E4%BF%A0-%E6%8E%A8%E6%96%B0%E6%AD%8C-%E6%9B%BF%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E9%AB%98%E5%91%BC-%E6%88%91%E5%94%94%E4%BF%82%E6%AD%BB%E8%A0%A2|title = 黎明化身「明福俠」推新歌 替港人高呼：我唔係死蠢 |publisher = 香港01 | date = 2016-07-28 |accessdate = 2020-02-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200206112423/https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/34000/%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87-%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E5%8C%96%E8%BA%AB-%E6%98%8E%E7%A6%8F%E4%BF%A0-%E6%8E%A8%E6%96%B0%E6%AD%8C-%E6%9B%BF%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E9%AB%98%E5%91%BC-%E6%88%91%E5%94%94%E4%BF%82%E6%AD%BB%E8%A0%A2|archive-date =2020-02-06|dead-url =no}}</ref>，2019年，黎明以明福俠身份創辦樂隊[[Gingerbread_(樂隊)|Gingerbread]]<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/983353-%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-%E6%98%8E%E7%A6%8F%E4%BF%A0%E8%AE%8ABand%E5%8F%8B+%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E5%A0%B1%E5%96%9C%E6%90%B5%E9%BD%8A%E9%9A%8A%E5%8F%8B%E8%AB%97%E6%A8%82%E9%9A%8A%E5%90%8D |title = 明福俠變Band友 黎明報喜搵齊隊友諗樂隊名 |publisher = 星島日報 |date = 2019-04-19 |accessdate =2020-02-06|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20190602062152/http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/983353-%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-%E6%98%8E%E7%A6%8F%E4%BF%A0%E8%AE%8ABand%E5%8F%8B+%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E5%A0%B1%E5%96%9C%E6%90%B5%E9%BD%8A%E9%9A%8A%E5%8F%8B%E8%AB%97%E6%A8%82%E9%9A%8A%E5%90%8D|archive-date =2019-06-02|dead-url =yes}}</ref>。

== 製作概念 ==
2016年初，黎明在社交網站[[facebook|facebook]]開設專頁，同年4月首次以明福俠身份在專頁亮相。明福俠是黎明創作的一個虛構人物，人物造型參考自蝙蝠俠，包括盔甲、由浴簾縫製而成的斗篷及面罩等<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1660065/%E6%98%8E%E7%A6%8F%E4%BF%A0%E7%94%A8%E8%88%8A%E6%B5%B4%E7%B0%BE%E5%81%9A%E6%96%97%E7%AF%B7|title = 明福俠用舊浴簾做斗篷|publisher = 晴報 |date = 2017-02-13 |accessdate =2020-02-07|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20200207090712/https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1660065/%E6%98%8E%E7%A6%8F%E4%BF%A0%E7%94%A8%E8%88%8A%E6%B5%B4%E7%B0%BE%E5%81%9A%E6%96%97%E7%AF%B7|archive-date =2017-02-07|dead-url =no}}</ref>，初時由黎明以真人方式演繹<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160712/bkn-20160712174631332-0712_00862_001.html|title = 些牙明福俠穿崩片 黎明忟爆：頂你個肺|publisher = 東方日報 |date = 2016-07-12 |accessdate =2020-02-07|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20170610041836/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160712/bkn-20160712174631332-0712_00862_001.html|archive-date =2017-06-10|dead-url =no}}</ref>，再以電腦效果加上盔甲、斗篷及面罩，與網民互動及交代工作近況，曾於同年9月及11月宣佈離開<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160909/bkn-20160909172059427-0909_00862_001.html|title = 「明福俠」宣布離開黎明|publisher = 東方日報 |date = 2016-09-09|accessdate =2020-02-08|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20170610034641/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160909/bkn-20160909172059427-0909_00862_001.html|archive-date =2017-06-10|dead-url =no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/article/20161115/s00016/1479146629810/%E6%98%8E%E7%A6%8F%E4%BF%A0%E8%84%AB%E9%9D%A2%E7%BD%A9%E8%A9%B1%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E|title = 明福俠脫面罩話離開黎明|publisher = 明報 |date = 2016-11-15 |accessdate =2020-02-08|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20200208080942/https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/article/20161115/s00016/1479146629810/%E6%98%8E%E7%A6%8F%E4%BF%A0%E8%84%AB%E9%9D%A2%E7%BD%A9%E8%A9%B1%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E|archive-date =2020-02-08|dead-url =no}}</ref>，但及後仍不定期亮相，多以電腦動畫方式呈現。2018，替黎明製作明福俠[[肖像|肖像]]的[[動畫師|動畫師]]，憑想像繪畫出黎明女兒的卡通肖像，大眾媒體稱為「明福囡」<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1350861/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E9%96%8B%E5%80%8B%E5%94%B1%E6%99%92%E5%8D%8A%E6%AD%B2%E5%A4%A7-%E6%98%8E%E7%A6%8F%E5%9B%A1-%E6%B4%BEB%E5%A5%B3%E8%82%96%E5%83%8F%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E5%93%81%E5%86%A7%E6%AD%8C%E8%BF%B7|title = 黎明開個唱晒半歲大「明福囡」 派B女肖像紀念品冧歌迷|publisher = 頭條日報 |date = 2018-10-28|accessdate =2020-02-07|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20200207124253/https://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1350861/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82-%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E9%96%8B%E5%80%8B%E5%94%B1%E6%99%92%E5%8D%8A%E6%AD%B2%E5%A4%A7-%E6%98%8E%E7%A6%8F%E5%9B%A1-%E6%B4%BEB%E5%A5%B3%E8%82%96%E5%83%8F%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E5%93%81%E5%86%A7%E6%AD%8C%E8%BF%B7|archive-date =2020-02-07|dead-url =yes}}</ref>。

== 音樂作品 ==
