== 其他作品 ==
2016至2017年間，明福俠以真人演繹及聲演方式擔任[[維他命|維他命]]產品[[代言人|代言人]]，參與演出電視廣告及平面廣告<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20161105/1478340380250/%E6%98%8E%E7%A6%8F%E4%BF%A0%E6%8B%8D%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%E7%8F%BE%E7%9C%9F%E8%BA%AB-%E7%9B%94%E7%94%B2send%E5%92%97%E5%8E%BB%E7%93%A6%E5%8A%AA%E9%98%BF%E5%9C%96%E4%B9%BE%E6%B4%97|title = 明福俠拍廣告現真身︰盔甲Send咗去瓦努阿圖乾洗|publisher = 明報 |date = 2016-11-05 |accessdate =2020-02-08|archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20200206111658/https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20161105/1478340380250/%E6%98%8E%E7%A6%8F%E4%BF%A0%E6%8B%8D%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%E7%8F%BE%E7%9C%9F%E8%BA%AB-%E7%9B%94%E7%94%B2send%E5%92%97%E5%8E%BB%E7%93%A6%E5%8A%AA%E9%98%BF%E5%9C%96%E4%B9%BE%E6%B4%97|archive-date =2020-02-06|dead-url =no}}</ref>。2017年，黎明參與香港首個emoji創意慈善企劃，親自設計出明福俠抱抱導盲犬的[[表情圖標|表情圖標]]，為[[香港導盲犬協會|香港導盲犬協會]]籌款<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |author = 馮仁昭 | url = https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20170213/19926407|title = 明福俠Emoji助導盲犬 |publisher = 蘋果日報 | date = 2017-02-13 |accessdate = 2020-02-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200208020609/https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20170213/19926407|archive-date =2020-02-08|dead-url =yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = http://paper.wenweipo.com/2017/02/13/EN1702130023.htm|title = 黎明化身明福俠宣揚導盲犬|publisher = 香港文匯報 | date = 2017-02-13 |accessdate = 2020-02-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200208020840/http://paper.wenweipo.com/2017/02/13/EN1702130023.htm|archive-date =2020-02-08|dead-url =no}}</ref>；2018年，黎明自創明福俠造型的紫色無花果餡月餅，並以明福俠身份透過真人及動畫方式演繹宣傳廣告<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%E8%87%AA%E8%AA%8D%E4%BF%82%E8%82%A5%E4%BB%94-%E6%98%8E%E7%A6%8F%E4%BF%A0%E9%9C%B2%E9%BB%9Esell%E6%9C%88%E9%A4%85-138099|title = 黎明自認係肥仔 明福俠露點sell月餅|publisher = am730 |date = 2018-08-16 |accessdate =2020-02-08|archive-url =https://web.archive.